  <brief_title>Open-label, Pharmacokinetic, Safety and Efficacy Study of Adjunctive Brivaracetam in Children With Epilepsy.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-Label, Single-Arm, Multicenter, Pharmacokinetic, Safety, and Efficacy Study of Adjunctive Administration of Brivaracetam in Subjects From ≥1 Month to &lt;16 Years Old With Epilepsy</official_title>
