  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Initial study in children with epilepsy to evaluate the pharmacokinetics, safety,
      tolerability and preliminary efficacy of adjunctive treatment with brivaracetam, and to
      develop dosing adaptations for future studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
